      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "546b88699c88996f",
      "text": "Glitch offers collaborative features that seem worth the effort to learn: you can immediately share the code with other hackers or even write code together directly; once installed in a remix of wiki-wiki, you can also immediately share the new behaviors or features you've created, or share the bugs where you can ask for more specific help. Your collaborators can remix what you've done and build on your work."
